ActAccessible Canada Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Employment and Social Development as the Minister for the Purposes of the Accessible Canada Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2023-1064 of October 27, 2023; and (2) designating the Minister of Employment and Social Development, a member of the King's Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the ACCESSIBLE CANADA ACT.
